235
00:17:20,340 --> 00:17:23,180
(Shen Shu)

236
00:17:23,200 --> 00:17:24,160
Who am I?

237
00:17:28,990 --> 00:17:29,920
Yes, who am I?

238
00:17:35,440 --> 00:17:38,200
Why am I in the Battle of Linyuan Pass?

239
00:17:40,790 --> 00:17:42,230
The Battle of Linyuan Pass.

240
00:17:45,360 --> 00:17:46,810
The Battle of Linyuan Pass?

241
00:17:50,120 --> 00:17:51,230
