286
00:21:55,120 --> 00:21:56,120
Ningyan!

287
00:21:57,200 --> 00:21:58,990
- Ningyan!
- Uncle!

288
00:22:01,990 --> 00:22:03,270
I cried for nothing!

289
00:22:04,230 --> 00:22:05,710
There, there. I'm fine.

290
00:22:06,360 --> 00:22:07,200
Ningyan...!

291
00:22:09,140 --> 00:22:11,900
(Haoqi Tower)

292
00:22:11,900 --> 00:22:17,460
(The Witcher's Sect)

293
00:22:36,960 --> 00:22:37,800
Father.

294
00:22:41,120 --> 00:22:43,470
He floated in the canal for over 10 days.

295
00:22:45,200 --> 00:22:46,400
Wait no more.

296
00:22:48,440 --> 00:22:49,790
Have his family

297
00:22:51,440 --> 00:22:52,550
bury him soon.

298
00:22:53,510 --> 00:22:54,350
Father,

299
00:22:54,790 --> 00:22:55,630
Xu Qi'an

300
00:22:55,880 --> 00:22:56,720
is back alive.

301
00:23:34,710 --> 00:23:36,160
Was that a dream?

302
00:23:37,750 --> 00:23:39,960
But why did I have such a strange one?

303
00:23:50,360 --> 00:23:51,200
Hello.

304
00:23:52,320 --> 00:23:53,310
Xu Ningyan,

305
00:23:53,670 --> 00:23:54,550
have you finished

306
00:23:54,960 --> 00:23:56,120
the rest of the poem?

307
00:23:57,960 --> 00:23:58,800
Soon.

308
00:23:58,800 --> 00:24:00,750
Didn't you promise
to work on it after the case?

309
00:24:00,750 --> 00:24:03,030
It's been 10 days. Where were you?

310
00:24:03,030 --> 00:24:04,300
Why didn't you return my message?

311
00:24:04,400 --> 00:24:05,240
I was dead.

312
00:24:07,990 --> 00:24:08,840
Xu Ningyan?

313
00:24:09,360 --> 00:24:10,200
Xu Ningyan?

314
00:24:40,130 --> 00:24:40,970
Hey,

315
00:24:41,260 --> 00:24:43,230
since when are you addicted to being a cat?

316
00:24:44,790 --> 00:24:46,640
Such a trifle doesn't matter.

317
00:24:47,470 --> 00:24:48,440
What brings you here?

318
00:24:49,750 --> 00:24:52,680
I heard you were
killed in action earlier today.

319
00:24:52,790 --> 00:24:53,680
I didn't believe it

320
00:24:53,920 --> 00:24:55,120
and came to see for myself.

321
00:24:55,680 --> 00:24:56,750
I knew it.

322
00:24:56,920 --> 00:24:59,510
You were dead physically,

323
00:24:59,640 --> 00:25:02,790
but I sensed subtle movements
of your primordial spirit.

324
00:25:03,400 --> 00:25:05,070
Then I gave you a hand

325
00:25:05,230 --> 00:25:07,790
to bring it back to your body.

326
00:25:10,160 --> 00:25:11,640
Thankfully, you came in time,

327
00:25:11,710 --> 00:25:13,710
or I'd be buried alive.

328
00:25:13,960 --> 00:25:14,990
I know, right?

329
00:25:15,310 --> 00:25:16,150
Thank you

330
00:25:17,160 --> 00:25:19,640
for saving my life.

331
00:25:22,510 --> 00:25:23,710
It's an equivalent exchange.

332
00:25:24,360 --> 00:25:25,920
You owe me one.

333
00:25:31,510 --> 00:25:32,800
Yes, of course.

334
00:25:34,790 --> 00:25:35,630
By the way,

335
00:25:35,790 --> 00:25:39,230
did you see No. 2, Li Miaozhen, in Yunzhou?

336
00:25:39,680 --> 00:25:40,750
She wasn't there.

337
00:25:40,920 --> 00:25:41,840
When I asked,

338
00:25:41,840 --> 00:25:44,230
she said she was on her way to the capital.

339
00:25:44,840 --> 00:25:47,160
I had meant to ask her for help,

340
00:25:47,160 --> 00:25:48,710
using her force to solve the case.

341
00:25:49,200 --> 00:25:50,550
With her assistance,

342
00:25:50,750 --> 00:25:52,920
I wouldn't have suffered so much.

343
00:25:55,710 --> 00:25:57,160
Looks like you were doomed

344
00:25:58,070 --> 00:26:00,030
to suffering.

345
00:26:02,270 --> 00:26:03,120
I'll show myself out.

346
00:26:05,510 --> 00:26:06,350
One more thing.

347
00:26:06,600 --> 00:26:07,440
What is it?

348
00:26:10,680 --> 00:26:11,840
Nice body.

349
00:26:17,540 --> 00:26:18,820
(Guardians)

350
00:26:20,360 --> 00:26:21,640
Summon Silver Gong Xu at once.

351
00:26:21,640 --> 00:26:22,510
Lord Wei asks for him.

352
00:26:22,840 --> 00:26:23,680
Yes.

353
00:26:27,750 --> 00:26:28,990
There you are.

354
00:26:29,120 --> 00:26:29,990
Others might think

355
00:26:29,990 --> 00:26:32,230
Father has adopted another son.

356
00:26:32,230 --> 00:26:33,310
Don't get in my way.

357
00:26:33,310 --> 00:26:34,640
You should've died in Yunzhou.

358
00:26:46,160 --> 00:26:47,200
He dodged my punch!

359
00:26:48,600 --> 00:26:49,550
How come?

360
00:26:50,960 --> 00:26:51,800
Lord Wei!

361
00:26:55,070 --> 00:26:56,270
Greetings, Lord Wei.

362
00:27:05,790 --> 00:27:06,630
Come.

363
00:27:10,400 --> 00:27:12,310
I read Song Tingfeng's report,

364
00:27:12,880 --> 00:27:15,070
saying you went missing
after capturing the rebels.

365
00:27:15,070 --> 00:27:16,920
You might've been killed.

366
00:27:17,200 --> 00:27:19,310
But I know how skilled you are.

367
00:27:19,600 --> 00:27:21,120
Most people can't kill you.

368
00:27:22,070 --> 00:27:24,160
I wasn't sure what that was,

369
00:27:24,840 --> 00:27:26,230
but it wasn't any rebel.

370
00:27:29,990 --> 00:27:32,230
Xu Qi'an...

371
00:27:35,510 --> 00:27:36,680
Xu Qi'an,

372
00:27:37,880 --> 00:27:39,990
any last words?

373
00:27:48,550 --> 00:27:49,390
Lord Wei,

374
00:27:50,030 --> 00:27:51,030
I'm confused.

375
00:27:51,600 --> 00:27:53,600
Was it Zhu Yang who killed me?

376
00:27:53,680 --> 00:27:56,640
He's sorting evidence against
the Guardians at the Ministry of War.

377
00:27:56,640 --> 00:27:57,780
How could he have killed you?

378
00:27:59,510 --> 00:28:00,350
Father,

379
00:28:00,400 --> 00:28:01,840
His Majesty summoned you urgently.

380
00:28:03,030 --> 00:28:03,880
The Ministry of War?

381
00:28:03,990 --> 00:28:04,830
Zhu Yang?

382
00:28:04,920 --> 00:28:05,660
Yes.

383
00:28:05,660 --> 00:28:07,710
When you were in Yunzhou
in the last three months,

384
00:28:07,710 --> 00:28:09,120
he switched sides and joined them.

385
00:28:09,310 --> 00:28:11,360
He, as a Gold Gong, accused us of corruption

386
00:28:11,360 --> 00:28:13,070
and bending the law before His Majesty.

387
00:28:13,270 --> 00:28:15,120
His Majesty ordered a thorough investigation.

388
00:28:15,230 --> 00:28:17,440
Two Gold Gongs and a dozen Copper Gongs

389
00:28:17,440 --> 00:28:18,980
were jailed by the Ministry of Justice.

390
00:28:19,920 --> 00:28:21,680
That was to retaliate against me.

391
00:28:24,310 --> 00:28:25,600
Are you affected, Lord Wei?

392
00:28:25,920 --> 00:28:26,760
No.

393
00:28:27,920 --> 00:28:29,510
That's a relief.

394
00:28:31,360 --> 00:28:33,270
Father's playing along.

395
00:28:33,470 --> 00:28:34,840
He's using Zhu Yang's attack

396
00:28:34,840 --> 00:28:37,750
to clean house in the Guardian Yamen.

397
00:28:38,070 --> 00:28:39,680
If that wasn't Zhu Yang,

398
00:28:40,400 --> 00:28:42,270
what exactly did I see?

399
00:28:42,360 --> 00:28:43,270
Hallucination.

400
00:28:43,750 --> 00:28:44,680
Hallucination?

401
00:28:46,310 --> 00:28:47,750
The 3rd-Rank Hypnotizer

402
00:28:48,200 --> 00:28:49,200
of The Witcher's Sect

403
00:28:49,680 --> 00:28:51,310
uses hallucination to kill.

404
00:28:51,990 --> 00:28:53,120
Once hypnotized,

405
00:28:53,600 --> 00:28:56,750
you'll be haunted by all the obsessions

406
00:28:56,990 --> 00:28:58,600
and fears you had,

407
00:28:58,920 --> 00:29:00,070
falling at his disposal.

408
00:29:04,640 --> 00:29:06,200
Hypnotizer?

409
00:29:08,200 --> 00:29:09,040
Lord Wei,

410
00:29:09,710 --> 00:29:11,750
I'm a nobody.

411
00:29:12,270 --> 00:29:14,440
It was beneath a 3rd-Rank Hypnotizer

412
00:29:14,440 --> 00:29:16,880
to kill me. Why did he do that?

413
00:29:17,200 --> 00:29:18,750
Had he meant to kill you,

414
00:29:20,200 --> 00:29:21,750
could you sit here with me now?

415
00:29:32,120 --> 00:29:32,960
Lord Wei,

416
00:29:33,360 --> 00:29:34,920
I still don't understand.

417
00:29:35,510 --> 00:29:36,550
Don't think too much.

418
00:29:37,160 --> 00:29:38,310
As a Guardian,

419
00:29:38,600 --> 00:29:40,230
just fulfill your duty.

420
00:29:41,470 --> 00:29:42,310
Remember,

421
00:29:42,920 --> 00:29:44,160
should the sky fall,

422
00:29:44,470 --> 00:29:45,790
I'll hold it for you.

423
00:29:46,840 --> 00:29:47,680
Yes.

424
00:29:49,120 --> 00:29:49,960
Wait,

425
00:29:50,680 --> 00:29:52,070
how did you come back to life?

426
00:29:52,990 --> 00:29:54,310
Jinlian of the Realm Sect...

427
00:29:54,310 --> 00:29:56,230
The Elixir of Life.

428
00:29:56,600 --> 00:29:58,840
You took the Elixir of Life
of the Astronomical Bureau.

429
00:30:00,310 --> 00:30:01,550
If someone asks,

430
00:30:01,960 --> 00:30:03,230
just say so,

431
00:30:04,160 --> 00:30:05,000
understand?

432
00:30:07,230 --> 00:30:08,070
Yes.

433
00:30:12,360 --> 00:30:13,310
Good day, Lord Wei.

434
00:30:14,750 --> 00:30:15,590
Wei Yuan,

435
00:30:15,790 --> 00:30:17,470
stop lying.

436
00:30:17,880 --> 00:30:19,470
Xu Qi'an couldn't have been

437
00:30:19,470 --> 00:30:21,750
brought back to life by the Elixir of Life.

438
00:30:22,070 --> 00:30:23,710
It's invaluable.

439
00:30:23,710 --> 00:30:25,680
Even His Majesty failed to obtain one.

440
00:30:26,030 --> 00:30:28,710
Never would the Bureau give it to Xu.

441
00:30:29,400 --> 00:30:30,600
Whether or not that's true,

442
00:30:30,990 --> 00:30:33,200
you may check with the Bureau,

443
00:30:33,470 --> 00:30:34,710
Your Majesty.

444
00:30:36,230 --> 00:30:37,070
Sure.

445
00:30:38,200 --> 00:30:40,360
Have someone go there to confirm it.

446
00:30:40,750 --> 00:30:41,640
Besides,

447
00:30:41,960 --> 00:30:43,230
the title of nobility

448
00:30:43,920 --> 00:30:45,270
is put on hold

449
00:30:45,680 --> 00:30:46,960
for the time being.

450
00:30:57,470 --> 00:30:59,440
Where's everyone?

451
00:30:59,880 --> 00:31:02,200
They used to act like my buddies

452
00:31:02,310 --> 00:31:04,750
but didn't come to my funeral.

453
00:31:05,310 --> 00:31:06,790
Let's drink after work.

454
00:31:07,310 --> 00:31:08,150
Go to the brothel!

455
00:31:08,160 --> 00:31:09,160
Yes, of course!

456
00:31:09,470 --> 00:31:10,360
You know what?

457
00:31:10,600 --> 00:31:12,310
Someone saw Xu Qi'an just now.

458
00:31:12,310 --> 00:31:13,960
- Saw him? No way.
- Impossible!

459
00:31:13,960 --> 00:31:15,230
His burial is today.

460
00:31:15,960 --> 00:31:18,600
Could that be his ghost?

461
00:31:18,880 --> 00:31:20,400
Ghosts can't come here.

462
00:31:20,400 --> 00:31:22,070
- Hey, I...
- Later. We aren't done yet.

463
00:31:22,680 --> 00:31:23,520
Truth be told,

464
00:31:23,520 --> 00:31:25,680
I never liked Xu Qi'an.

465
00:31:26,550 --> 00:31:27,710
He beat me at gambling,

466
00:31:27,710 --> 00:31:28,710
drinking,

467
00:31:28,840 --> 00:31:30,310
and work.

468
00:31:30,440 --> 00:31:31,470
I'm glad he died.

469
00:31:31,470 --> 00:31:32,990
-Yes!
- That's right.

470
00:31:38,680 --> 00:31:39,750
Who is this?

471
00:31:39,750 --> 00:31:40,710
Save your trick.

472
00:31:40,710 --> 00:31:41,990
Who is this?

473
00:31:45,990 --> 00:31:47,750
Xu...

474
00:31:47,750 --> 00:31:49,360
Mr. Xu!

475
00:31:52,640 --> 00:31:53,960
Mr. Xu's become a zombie!

476
00:31:53,960 --> 00:31:54,800
Run!

477
00:32:05,710 --> 00:32:06,790
A zombie!

478
00:32:14,120 --> 00:32:19,550
Who was glad I died?

479
00:32:19,680 --> 00:32:20,840
Him!

480
00:32:28,840 --> 00:32:30,790
Was it you?

481
00:32:35,070 --> 00:32:35,960
I'm sorry.

482
00:32:36,790 --> 00:32:37,960
Alright, alright.

483
00:32:38,990 --> 00:32:40,190
Mr. Xu...

484
00:32:40,510 --> 00:32:41,510
Didn't you

485
00:32:42,710 --> 00:32:43,680
die earlier?

486
00:32:44,680 --> 00:32:45,520
Yes.

487
00:32:47,510 --> 00:32:48,840
I forgot to introduce myself.

488
00:32:49,120 --> 00:32:50,640
I'm Xu Qi'an's twin brother,

489
00:32:50,640 --> 00:32:51,480
Xu Ba'an.

490
00:32:51,750 --> 00:32:54,270
I'll take over his post by Lord Wei's order.

491
00:32:54,550 --> 00:32:55,440
I have a question.

492
00:32:56,440 --> 00:32:57,840
Where are those of the Breeze Hall?

493
00:32:57,840 --> 00:32:59,200
They... they went to

494
00:32:59,710 --> 00:33:00,880
Yunzhou.

495
00:33:01,120 --> 00:33:01,960
Yunzhou?

496
00:33:02,400 --> 00:33:03,470
Why did they go there?

497
00:33:03,790 --> 00:33:07,640
Hearing your brother died there,
Gold Gong Yang and Silver Gong Li

498
00:33:07,840 --> 00:33:08,920
were grieved and furious.

499
00:33:08,920 --> 00:33:09,990
They blamed themselves.

500
00:33:09,990 --> 00:33:13,710
They gathered all their members before dawn

501
00:33:14,120 --> 00:33:15,120
to go to Yunzhou.

502
00:33:15,270 --> 00:33:17,070
They meant to avenge your brother's death

503
00:33:18,120 --> 00:33:19,070
on all the rebels

504
00:33:19,070 --> 00:33:20,840
and The Witcher's Sect.

505
00:33:25,750 --> 00:33:26,710
It's all set.

506
00:33:30,920 --> 00:33:32,030
Ningyan,

507
00:33:32,270 --> 00:33:33,510
rest in peace!

508
00:33:33,510 --> 00:33:34,640
We're going to Yunzhou

509
00:33:34,750 --> 00:33:37,310
to wipe out the remnants
of The Witcher's Sect

510
00:33:38,750 --> 00:33:40,640
to avenge your death.

511
00:33:42,440 --> 00:33:43,280
Mr. Yang,

512
00:33:43,440 --> 00:33:44,440
we're ready.

513
00:33:51,270 --> 00:33:52,200
Set sail.

514
00:34:39,590 --> 00:34:41,550
You robbed others, huh?

515
00:34:42,070 --> 00:34:44,240
You bullied others, huh?

516
00:34:44,960 --> 00:34:47,070
You abused others, huh?

517
00:34:48,030 --> 00:34:50,190
You assaulted others, huh?

518
00:34:50,840 --> 00:34:52,110
Listen carefully.

519
00:34:52,670 --> 00:34:53,670
If you do that again,

520
00:34:54,240 --> 00:34:55,550
I'll break your legs.

521
00:34:55,960 --> 00:34:57,280
We won't do it again.

522
00:34:57,510 --> 00:34:58,960
Please spare us, Miss.

523
00:34:59,880 --> 00:35:00,720
Get lost.

524
00:35:01,030 --> 00:35:01,870
Yes, Miss.

525
00:35:04,590 --> 00:35:06,150
Aren't you bold

526
00:35:06,240 --> 00:35:07,190
to carry a saber again?

527
00:35:07,510 --> 00:35:08,350
No, no.

528
00:35:08,360 --> 00:35:09,200
It's yours.

529
00:35:09,210 --> 00:35:10,060
All yours.

530
00:35:14,400 --> 00:35:15,240
Master,

531
00:35:15,960 --> 00:35:17,110
you're amazing!

532
00:35:17,240 --> 00:35:18,080
You bet.

533
00:35:18,150 --> 00:35:18,990
Let's go.

534
00:35:24,240 --> 00:35:27,510
Good job. You've stopped injustice 88 times.

535
00:35:28,190 --> 00:35:29,110
Be accurate.

536
00:35:29,190 --> 00:35:30,630
It's 89 times.

537
00:35:30,800 --> 00:35:33,190
I acted twice when passing by Mount Wushan.

538
00:35:33,960 --> 00:35:35,320
You're the best!

539
00:35:36,720 --> 00:35:37,840
However,

540
00:35:37,960 --> 00:35:39,800
you're fighting constantly on the way.

541
00:35:39,800 --> 00:35:41,720
When can we get to the Dafeng?

542
00:35:42,070 --> 00:35:43,920
We could've arrived in three days by mount.

543
00:35:43,920 --> 00:35:44,840
As of now,

544
00:35:44,990 --> 00:35:46,670
we've wasted over three months.

545
00:35:46,990 --> 00:35:47,840
Waste?

546
00:35:48,320 --> 00:35:49,800
We didn't waste our time.

547
00:35:49,920 --> 00:35:52,070
This trip is to see the world
and train ourselves.

548
00:35:52,320 --> 00:35:53,470
See the world?

549
00:35:54,110 --> 00:35:56,470
I thought it was to solve my problem.

550
00:35:58,720 --> 00:35:59,880
Yes, that too.

551
00:36:02,470 --> 00:36:04,440
Your problem matters the most.

552
00:36:07,720 --> 00:36:08,560
No. 3?

553
00:36:09,150 --> 00:36:10,960
Yes, that's right. Four of my friends

554
00:36:11,150 --> 00:36:12,670
sailed to Yunzhou.

555
00:36:12,920 --> 00:36:14,280
Please keep an eye on them.

556
00:36:15,320 --> 00:36:17,630
I'll let you know their looks later.

557
00:36:17,630 --> 00:36:19,440
Yunzhou has been unsafe lately.

558
00:36:19,440 --> 00:36:20,800
It is, right?

559
00:36:20,990 --> 00:36:23,190
They mean to raid The Witcher's Sect.

560
00:36:23,400 --> 00:36:25,070
What are they thinking?

561
00:36:25,880 --> 00:36:27,030
If you find them,

562
00:36:27,190 --> 00:36:29,670
tell them Xu Qi'an didn't die.

563
00:36:29,670 --> 00:36:31,510
Don't act rashly and return to

564
00:36:31,510 --> 00:36:32,800
the capital at once.

565
00:36:34,920 --> 00:36:36,840
But I'm right outside the capital.

566
00:36:37,250 --> 00:36:38,110
Don't worry.

567
00:36:38,110 --> 00:36:40,070
I'll relay your message by a carrier pigeon.

568
00:36:40,840 --> 00:36:41,680
Alright.

569
00:36:42,140 --> 00:36:42,980
Wait,

570
00:36:42,990 --> 00:36:45,280
when I arrive, I need a favor from you.

571
00:36:45,280 --> 00:36:46,120
Where can I find you?

572
00:36:46,670 --> 00:36:47,920
Find me?

573
00:36:49,150 --> 00:36:50,550
What's wrong? You won't help me?

574
00:36:50,840 --> 00:36:52,960
Don't forget you still owe me one.

575
00:36:58,400 --> 00:37:00,360
I... I know.

576
00:37:00,960 --> 00:37:03,360
You see, the Spring Exam is near.

577
00:37:03,360 --> 00:37:05,880
I've been too busy studying at school

578
00:37:05,880 --> 00:37:07,720
to see you.

579
00:37:07,990 --> 00:37:09,920
How about you go to see my brother?

580
00:37:10,440 --> 00:37:11,280
Your brother?

581
00:37:12,070 --> 00:37:13,510
My brother, Xu Qi'an,

582
00:37:13,510 --> 00:37:14,510
is a Guardian.

583
00:37:14,510 --> 00:37:16,280
He's much better than me.

584
00:37:16,280 --> 00:37:17,440
He's extremely smart,

585
00:37:17,440 --> 00:37:18,670
and sharp.

586
00:37:18,840 --> 00:37:21,400
Also, he's good-looking

587
00:37:21,400 --> 00:37:22,960
- charming...
- That's enough.

588
00:37:23,110 --> 00:37:24,150
Where can I find him?

589
00:37:24,840 --> 00:37:26,550
Just go to the Guardian Yamen.

590
00:37:27,240 --> 00:37:28,240
Ningyan, Ningyan!

591
00:37:28,240 --> 00:37:29,720
Caiwei is here to see you.

592
00:37:29,920 --> 00:37:31,150
Sorry, I have to go.

593
00:37:31,470 --> 00:37:32,590
Remember to relay my message.

594
00:37:35,070 --> 00:37:35,910
No. 3?

595
00:37:36,590 --> 00:37:37,440
No. 3?

596
00:37:38,360 --> 00:37:40,360
He seems so unreliable.

597
00:37:40,760 --> 00:37:42,240
We're doing our best to help him,

598
00:37:42,240 --> 00:37:43,110
but look at him

599
00:37:43,190 --> 00:37:44,510
pushing us to someone else.

600
00:37:44,960 --> 00:37:47,280
How dare he brush me off!

601
00:37:47,630 --> 00:37:48,880
Xu Qi'an, huh?

602
00:37:49,360 --> 00:37:51,320
I'll show him what I'm capable of.

603
00:37:51,800 --> 00:37:52,640
Let's go!

604
00:37:52,670 --> 00:37:54,150
Beat more bag guys to vent my anger.

605
00:37:54,720 --> 00:37:56,360
Make it 90 times then.

606
00:37:58,720 --> 00:37:59,560
Caiwei,

607
00:37:59,800 --> 00:38:00,800
what brings you here?

608
00:38:01,550 --> 00:38:02,390
Taste it.

609
00:38:07,510 --> 00:38:09,360
I'm here for two matters.

610
00:38:09,510 --> 00:38:10,800
One,

611
00:38:12,030 --> 00:38:13,370
don't go to the Bureau these days.

612
00:38:13,760 --> 00:38:15,110
Hearing that you came back to life,

613
00:38:15,110 --> 00:38:16,550
everyone at the Bureau was shocked.

614
00:38:16,630 --> 00:38:17,800
They couldn't wait to see you,

615
00:38:17,800 --> 00:38:19,030
but I stopped them.

616
00:38:21,070 --> 00:38:22,360
So...

617
00:38:22,800 --> 00:38:23,980
how did you come back to life?

618
00:38:28,550 --> 00:38:29,880
I...

619
00:38:31,590 --> 00:38:33,990
I took the Elixir of Life.

620
00:38:35,670 --> 00:38:37,280
The Elixir of Life.

621
00:38:38,030 --> 00:38:39,440
Do you even know what that is?

622
00:38:40,240 --> 00:38:43,240
It takes the Bureau 60 years to make one.

623
00:38:43,340 --> 00:38:44,190
If you're dying,

624
00:38:44,190 --> 00:38:45,880
take that elixir and you'll live.

625
00:38:46,670 --> 00:38:48,720
If those of the 7th Rank take it,

626
00:38:48,840 --> 00:38:50,240
they'll reach higher ranks.

627
00:38:50,760 --> 00:38:52,960
How could a humble Guardian like you

628
00:38:53,240 --> 00:38:55,550
gain such an elixir?

629
00:38:59,510 --> 00:39:00,880
Because

630
00:39:01,720 --> 00:39:02,760
I...

631
00:39:02,960 --> 00:39:04,190
Because I...

632
00:39:04,190 --> 00:39:05,800
Because you

633
00:39:05,920 --> 00:39:08,110
got it from me.

634
00:39:09,190 --> 00:39:10,040
My master gave me this

635
00:39:10,040 --> 00:39:12,190
when I first joined the Bureau.

636
00:39:12,360 --> 00:39:13,720
It's been with me in this pouch

637
00:39:13,720 --> 00:39:14,840
for 10 years.

638
00:39:18,800 --> 00:39:21,360
So that's yours.

639
00:39:24,070 --> 00:39:26,400
That leads to my second matter.

640
00:39:26,400 --> 00:39:27,470
My Elixir of Life

641
00:39:28,670 --> 00:39:30,590
is now yours.

642
00:39:33,470 --> 00:39:34,870
I don't know why, but Master

643
00:39:34,870 --> 00:39:35,840
had me bring it to you,

644
00:39:35,840 --> 00:39:36,760
so here I am.

645
00:39:38,920 --> 00:39:39,990
You have to pay me back.

646
00:39:40,190 --> 00:39:41,440
If you invent other rarities

647
00:39:41,440 --> 00:39:42,760
such as chicken powder,

648
00:39:42,760 --> 00:39:43,610
you have to tell me.

649
00:39:43,610 --> 00:39:44,710
It's an equivalent exchange.

650
00:39:44,760 --> 00:39:45,600
You got it.

651
00:39:45,610 --> 00:39:46,480
Thanks.

652
00:39:51,720 --> 00:39:52,590
It's really good.

653
00:39:52,590 --> 00:39:53,920
Give me the recipe later.

654
00:39:53,920 --> 00:39:55,070
- No problem.
